		<title>06Entertainment in the area</title>
		<content>                                       
                                       
  There is no organised entertainment  
 such as discos or cinemas in this     
 area.                                 
  Christmas Whist Drives are popular at
 the village halls, and sometimes a    
 darts match is arranged at one or     
 other of the public houses.           
  Scotton Village Hall can be hired for
 private functions.                    
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
